Genesis:
“Juda, oweteni biro paki;
 bende inimak wasiki gi ngʼutgi,
 kendo oweteni biro kuloreni.

“Benjamin en ondiek ma kech kayo;
 gima osenego ochamo gokinyi,
 kendo godhiambo okidho matindo tindo gima osemako.”

Exodus:
Jodong Edom kibaji biro goyo,
 bende jotend Moab biro tetni,
 to jo-Kanaan chunygi biro nyosore;

Numbers:
Magi e joma chwo mane okaw koa kuom yawuot Josef:
 koa kuom Efraim, kaw Elishama wuod Amihud;
 koa kuom Manase, kaw Gamaliel wuod Pedazur;

Mano emomiyo jochuog wer nowero niya,
 “Bi Heshbon mondo mi ogere kendo;
 mad dala maduongʼ mar Sihon ochal kaka chon.

Eka Balaam nohulo ote moa kuom Nyasaye kama:
 Aa malo, Balak, kendo ichik iti;
 winja, wuod Zipor.

Pi ma aa e dapigeni biro pongʼ mao oko;
 kendo kothgi nochal gi pi mabubni.
  “Ruodhgi nobed gi teko moloyo Agag;
 pinyruodhgi notingʼ malo.

“Nyasaye nogologi Misri;
 kendo gin gi teko machalo mar jowi.
 Gikidho oganda jowasikgi
 kendo gituro chokegi matindo tindo;
 kendo gichwowogi gi aserni mag-gi.

“Anene, to ok sani;
 asudo machiegni, to ok bute.
 Sulwe biro wuok koa kuom Jakobo;
 ludh loch biro wuok ei Israel.
 Obiro toyo wiye jo-Moab,
 kod wiye yawuot Sheth duto.

Obiro loyo piny jo-Edom e lweny mi okaw;
 kendo Seir ma wasike, nokaw,
 to Israel nomed bedo motegno.

Eka noneno jo-Keni kendo ochiwo oteneni:
 “Kar dak mari nigi kwe,
 kari mar pondo ni e bwo lwanda;

Yiedhi madongo mathoth nobi koa e dho nam mar Kitim;
 gibiro mako Ashur kod Eber,
 to kata gin bende ibiro tiekgi.”

Nyikwa Reuben, ma en wuod Israel makayo, ne gin:
 kokadho kuom Hanok, ne gin joka Hanok;
 kokadho kuom Palu, ne gin joka Palu;

Nyikwa Simeon kaluwore gi anywola margi ne gin:
 koa kuom Nemuel, joka Nemuel;
 koa kuom Jamin, joka Jamin;
 koa kuom Jakin, joka Jakin;

Nyikwa Gad kaluwore gi anywola margi ne gin:
 koa kuom Zefon, joka Zefon;
 koa kuom Hagai, joka Hagi;
 koa kuom Shuni, joka Shuni;

Nyikwa Juda kaluwore gi anywola margi ne gin:
 koa kuom Shela, joka Shela;
 koa kuom Perez, joka Perez;
 koa kuom Zera, joka Zera.

Nyikwa Perez ne gin:
 koa kuom Hezron, joka Hezron;
 koa kuom Hamul, kod joka Hamul.

Nyikwa Isakar kaluwore gi anywola margi ne gin:
 koa kuom Tola, joka Tola;
 koa kuom Pua, joka Pua;

Nyikwa Zebulun kaluwore gi anywola margi ne gin:
 koa kuom Sered, joka Sered;
 koa kuom Elon, joka Elon;
 koa kuom Jalel, joka Jalel.

Nyikwa Manase ne gin:
 koa kuom Makir, joka Makir (Makir ne en wuod Gilead);
 koa kuom Gilead, joka Gilead.

Nyikwa Gilead e magi:
 koa kuom Iezer, joka Iezer;
 koa kuom Helek, joka Helek;

Nyikwa Efraim kaluwore gi anywola margi e magi:
 koa kuom Shuthela, joka Shuthela;
 koa kuom Beker, joka Beker;
 koa kuom Tahan, joka Tahan.

Nyikwa Benjamin kaluwore gi anywola margi ne gin:
 koa kuom Bela, joka Bela;
 koa kuom Ashbel, joka Ashbel;
 koa kuom Ahiram, joka Ahiram;

Nyikwa Bela kokalo kuom Ard gi Naaman ne gin:
 koa kuo Ard, joka Ard;
 koa kuom Naaman, joka Naaman.

Nyikwa Asher kaluwore gi anywola margi ne gin:
 koa kuom Imna, joka Imna;
 koa kuom Ishvi, joka Ishvi;
 koa kuom Beria, joka Beria;

kendo koa kuom nyikwa Beria ne gin:
 joka Heber;
 kod joka Malkiel.

Nyikwa Naftali kaluwore gi anywola margi ne gin:
 koa kuom Jazel, joka Jazel;
 koa kuom Guni, joka Guni;

Jo-Lawi mane okwan kaluwore gi anywola ne gin:
 koa kuom Gershon, joka Gershon;
 koa kuom Kohath, joka Kohath;
 koa kuom Merari, joka Merari.

Judges:
“Winjuru, un ruodhi! Chikuru itu, un jotelo!
 Abiro pako Jehova Nyasaye ka awerne;
 anachuog ne Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasach Israel wer.

I Samuel:
“Onge ngʼama ler ka Jehova Nyasaye;
 kendo onge moro makmana in;
 onge Lwanda machal gi Nyasachwa.

Obiro chiko tiende joge maler
 to joricho to nolal ei mudho.
  “Ngʼato ok lochi mana nikech teko;

II Samuel:
Nowacho ni:
 “Jehova Nyasaye en lwandana,
 en ohingana kendo en e jaresna;

Piny notetni kendo oyiengni,
 mise mag polo noyiengni;
 negitetni nikech nokecho.

Iro nowuok e ume;
 mach mangʼangʼni nowuokie dhoge,
 mirni maliel maliet bende nowuok kuome.

“Yor Nyasaye en yo malongʼo;
 wach Jehova Nyasaye onge ketho.
 En okumba ni jogo duto mopondo kuome.

“Iseresa e lwet jowa mane monja;
 iserita kaka jatelo mar ogendini.
 Joma ne ok angʼeyo nobet e bwo lochna,

ma gonya e lwet wasika.
 Nitingʼa malo moloyo wasika;
 ne iresa e lwet jo-mahundu.

“Jehova Nyasaye kelo resruok maduongʼ ne ruoth moketo;
 onyiso ngʼwonone mogundho ma ok rum ne ngʼate mowir,
 ni Daudi gi nyikwaye nyaka chiengʼ.”

II Kings:
Enodogi mana gi yo mane obirogo;
 kendo ok enodonj e dala maduongʼni,
 Jehova Nyasaye ema owacho.

I Chronicles:
Magi e yawuot Daudi mane onywolo ka en Hebron:
  Amnon wuode makayo wuod Ahinoam nyar Jezreel,
 mar ariyo ne en Daniel wuod Abigael nyar Karmel;

Ibneia wuod Jeroham;
 Ela wuod Uzi, wuod Mikri
 kod Meshulam wuod Shefatia, wuod Reuel, wuod Ibnija.

Jogi ne gin: Ahiezer ma jatendgi gi Joash owadgi ma yawuot Shema ja-Gibea,
 kod Jeziel gi Pelet yawuot Azmaveth;
 Beraka gi Jehu jo-Anathoth,

Nyikwa Lawi mamoko e magi:
  Koa kuom yawuot Amram noyier Shubael;
 koa kuom yawuot Shubael noyier Jedeya.

Yawuot Shemaya ne gin,
 Othni, Refael, Obed kod Elzabad;
 Elihu kod Semakia ma wedene bende ne joma niginyalo.

Jotend dhout Israel ne gin:
  koa kuom jo-Reuben: Eliezer wuod Zikri notelonegi,
 koa kuom jo-Simeon: Shefatia wuod Maaka notelonegi;

Ezra:
nyikwa Finehas,
 Gershom;
 nyikwa Ithamar,
 Daniel;
 nyikwa Daudi,
 Hatush

nyikwa Shekania;
 nyikwa Parosh,
 Zekaria, kaachiel kode ji mia achiel gi piero abich;

Nehemiah:
Jo-Juda kod jo-Benjamin bende nodak Jerusalem.
  Koa kuom nyikwa Juda ne gin:
 Athaya wuod Uzia, ma wuod Zekaria, ma wuod Amaria, ma wuod Shefatia, ma wuod Mahalalel, ma nyakwar Perez;

Matania wuod Mika, wuod Zabdi, wuod Asaf, notelo ne dwoko erokamano ni Nyasaye kod lamo;
 gi Bakbukia mane jatelo mar ariyo e kind jotich kaachiel kode;
 kod Abda wuod Shamua, wuod Galal, wuod Jeduthun.

E ndalo Joyakim, jodolo mane jotend dhoudi ne gin:
  koa e anywola Seraya ne en Meraya;
 koa e anywola Jeremia ne en Hanania;

Job:
Odiechiengno mad lokre mudho;
 mad Nyasaye man malo kik dewe;
 mad ler moro amora kik rieny kuome.

Mad odiechiengno otim luoch kendo mudho mandiwa oime;
 boche polo mondo oume;
 kendo wangʼ chiengʼ otim mudho.

Otienono, mad olal e mudho mandiwa;
 kik obed kaka achiel kuom odiechienge mag higa,
 kendo kik kwane kaka achiel kuom odiechienge mag dwe.

Mad sulwege mokinyi lokre mudho;
 mad piny mogeno ni biro ru tamre,
 kendo kik one ka ugwe chako wangʼ,

Iningʼe ni hembi oriti maber;
 inikwan mwanduni achiel achiel,
 kendo ok niyud kaonge moro kuomgi molal.

Aserni mag Jehova Nyasaye Maratego osechwoyo denda,
 ringra opongʼ gi kwiri marach ma asernigo okelo;
 kendo masiche mag Nyasaye olwora koni gi koni.

Kotimona kamano eka chunya noyud hoch,
 anabed gi kwe, kata obedo ni an gi rem malit;
 nikech ok asedagi weche mag Ngʼama Ler.

“Emomiyo ok anyal lingʼ;
 abiro wacho lit manie chunya,
 abiro nyiso pek ma an-go e chunya nikech mirima ma an-go.

“Aol gi ngima;
 mano emomiyo ok abi lingʼ ma ok awuoyo,
 to abiro wacho lit duto manie chunya.

Ikelo joneno manyien mondo okweda
 kendo imedo bedo mager koda;
 jolweny magi monja mana ka apaka magingore.

To wenge joma timbegi richo biro jony
 kendo yore mag tony biro lalnegi;
 to geno margi biro lal nono.”

Kata kamano an bende an gi paro machal gi ma un-go;
 kik upar ni afuwo.
 Uparo ni en ngʼa ma ok ongʼeyo weche ma uwachogi?

“Asedoko gima inyiero e dier osiepena,
 kata obedo ni an ngʼama kare kendo maonge ketho;
 to chon an ema ne Nyasaye winjo ywakna kendo dwoka!

Irido tiendena gi nyororo;
 kendo iluwo bangʼa e yorena maluwo duto,
 koketo kido e bwo tienda mondo onyis kamoro amora maluwo.

Ndalo dhano nosekwan chon;
 isechano kar romb dwechene,
 kendo iseketo gikone ma ok onyal kalo.

Ihewe dichiel kendo mogik, kendo olal nono;
 iloko kit wangʼe,
 kendo igole e dier ji chuth.

Ji ngʼamo dhogi ka gijara;
 Githalo lemba ka gisin koda,
 kendo ginur kuoma giduto ka giriwona.

Gik moko duto ne dhina maber, to koro osetieka;
 mi omaka gi ngʼuta kendo otura matindo tindo.
 Osechoma tir;

Jolweny mage pangore kochoma gi tekregi duto;
 gigona agengʼa ka gidwaro kedo koda,
 kendo giguro hembegi e alwora mar dalana.

to un bende asiemou ni ibiro kumou;
 nikech paro marach ma un-gono,
 eka unungʼe ni nitiere chiengʼ ngʼado bura.”

Kata bed ni oseyako mwandu mangʼeny kamano;
 to mwandugo ema biro kelone masira;
 kendo midhiero maduongʼ biro biro kuome mi hewe.

“To kata kamano, donge joricho manok ema tho piyo?
 Donge ji matin kuomgi kende ema masira mako;
 ma en masira ma mirimb Nyasaye ema okelo?

Ka ler mar odiechiengʼ rumo aruma nii,
 to janek aa malo kendo onego jochan gi jodhier;
 otimo kamano gotieno kolidho ka jakuo.

Wangʼ jachode bende rito mondo piny oimre;
 oparo e chunye niya, ‘Onge ngʼat ma biro nena,’
 kendo opando wangʼe mondo kik ngʼeye.

Jokuo turo udi gotieno,
 to kochopo odiechiengʼ to gipondo;
 nimar ok gidwar neno ler.

“To kata kamano gichalo buoyo moyienyo ewi pi malo;
 lopegi okwongʼ,
 maonge ngʼama rawo e puothegi mag mzabibu mi yudie olemo.

Gineno maber kuom kinde matin kende to bangʼe gilal nono kadiemo wangʼ,
 kendo ichokogi mi giner ka buya mopudhi;
 kendo ingʼadogi oko mana kaka ingʼado wiye cham.

To magi gin mana dir tijene ma oko kende;
 kendo gin mana gik manok kende mikuodho kuome!
 Koro en ngʼa mongʼeyo gima Nyasaye nyalo timo gi tekone?”

Kata ne bed ni nyithinde ngʼeny manade,
 to ligangla ema ochomogi;
 kendo nyithinde ok noyud chiemo moromogi nyaka chiengʼ.

Opowo kor gode modhi mabor gi kuonde ma ji odakie,
 mochop nyaka kuonde ma ji ok wuothie;
 ka giliero e tonde marundore koni gi koni.

Ngʼama ne chiegni tho nogwedha;
 kendo namiyo chuny dhako
 ma chwore otho duogo mi ower gi mor.

An ema ne anyisogi yo monego gilu kendo nabedo kaka ruodhgi;
 ne achalo ruoth e dier jokedo mage;
 bende ne achalo ngʼat mahoyo joma ywak.”

Pien denda lokore maratengʼ to ok nikech chiengʼ marieny matek;
 achungʼ e dier chokruok,
 kendo aywak mondo okonya.

Uwinjo, ne arito mondi kane uwuoyo,
 ne achiko ita ne wecheu mukwano ni nigi rieko;
 kinde mane umanyo weche monego uwachi,

ne achikonu ita adimba kinde mane uwuoyo,
 to onge ngʼato kuomu moseyudo Ayub gi ketho;
 kendo onge ngʼato kuomu mosedwoko weche Ayub.

Owuoyo gi ji e lek,
 kata e fweny gotieno seche ma dhano ni e nindo matut,
 ka giyweyo e otendnigi;

Joma roteke tho apoya e dier otieno;
 inegogi mi gilal nono,
 kendo igologi e dier ji, to ok gi lwet dhano.

Puonja mondo ane gik mopondona;
 kapo asetimo gimoro marach,
 to ok abi achak atim kamano kendo!’

Koro onge ngʼama nyalo rango wangʼ chiengʼ tir,
 nikech polo olendo kendo orieny makech;
 yamo oseriembo boche duto moweyo kor polo nono.

Koro aa malo ka dichwo;
 mondo idwoka weche,
 madwaro penjigi.

“Ne iwachona ni, ‘Koro chik iti mondo iwinj gima awacho;
 abiro penji penjo,
 kendo ibiro dwoka.’

Psalms:
Abiro hulo chenro mag Jehova Nyasaye ma ok lokre:
 Nowachona niya, “In wuoda;
 kawuono asedoko wuonu.

Yie iwinj dwonda gokinyi, yaye Jehova Nyasaye;
 aketo kwayona e nyimi gokinyi,
 kendo arito dwoko ka an gi geno.

Itieko joma wacho miriambo;
 Jehova Nyasaye ok mor gi joma dwaro chwero remo,
 kod jo-miriambo.

Kata wach achiel mowuok e dho jogi ok nyal gen;
 chunygi opongʼ gi kethruok.
 Dwondgi chalo gi liel mapok oum;
 lewgi olony e wacho miriambo.

Kecha, yaye Jehova Nyasaye, nikech aol;
 changa, yaye Jehova Nyasaye,
 nikech chokena rama malit.

to yie ni wasikano mondo olawa mi juka;
 we ginyon ngimana piny e lowo,
 mi gimi anind e buru mar lowo.  Sela

Ka ok oloko pache
 to obiro piago liganglane;
 obiro dolo okumbane mi otwe tondene.

Kethruok mosiko osejuko jasigu,
 isemuko miechgi madongo;
 kendo wi ji osewil kodgi.

Wer wende pak ne Jehova Nyasaye,
 mobet e kom lochne e Sayun;
 hul ni ogendini gik mosetimo.

Yorene dhi maber kinde duto,
 okawore omiyo chikeni ni mabor moyombe;
 ojaro wasike duto.

Okiyo ji kokichore ka sibuor mopondo;
 okichore mar mako joma ok nyal mondo ohinygi,
 omako joma ok nyal kendo oywayogi oko gi tonde mar meko.

Tur bad ngʼama rach ma timbene richo;
 luonge mondo onyis ji gik maricho mosetimo lingʼ-lingʼ,
 ma ji ok nyal fwenyo mi ngʼe.

Jehova Nyasaye ni e hekalu mare maler;
 Jehova Nyasaye ni e kom duongʼ mare manie polo.
 Orango timbe yawuot ji;
 wengene nonogi matut.

Obiro chwero
 mach maliel mager kod salfa kuom joma timbegi richo;
 yamo maliet ha matwoyo gik moko, biro kudhogi.

Nikech Jehova Nyasaye en Ngʼama Kare,
 kendo ohero adiera;
 joma timbegi oriere biro neno wangʼe.

Kony ji yaye Jehova Nyasaye,
 nikech joma oluoro Nyasaye koro onge;
 joma jo-adiera oserumo e dier ji.

mawacho niya, “Wabiro wuoyo kaka wahero;
 kendo onge ngʼama biro tamowa.
 Koso en ngʼa ma ruodhwa manyalo tamowa timo kamano?”

Bende joma timo timbe maricho dipuonjre adier?
  Gin joma kidho joga kaka ji chamo kuon;
 kendo gin joma ok luong Jehova Nyasaye mondo okonygi.

Isenyisa yor ngima;
 inipongʼa gi mor mogundho ka an e nyimi,
 kendo gi mor mosiko e badi korachwich.

Kata obedo ni inono chunya kendo itema gotieno,
 kata ka itema to ok ibi yudo gimoro kuoma;
 asengʼado e chunya ni dhoga ok bi timo richo.

E chandruok ne aluongo Jehova Nyasaye;
 ne aywak ne Nyasaye mondo okonya.
 Ne owinjo dwonda gie hekalu mare;
 ywakna nochopo e nyime, modonjo e ite.

Piny notetni kendo oyiengni;
 kendo mise mag gode notetni;
 ne gikirni nikech ne okecho.

Iro nodum koa e otuchi mag ume;
 mach mangʼangʼni nodhuolore kawuok e dhoge,
 kendo makaa maliel mager nobebni kawuok kuome.

Isemiya okumba mar warruokni,
 kendo lweti korachwich osesira;
 kony mari osemiyo abedo gi duongʼ.

Ne iresa e ywaruok gi ji.
 Ne iketa jatend ogendini;
 joma ne ok angʼeyo chon notiyona.

mane oresa e lwet wasika;
 ne itingʼa malo e kind wasika
 ne iresa e lwet jo-mahundu.

Owuok gie tungʼ polo konchiel,
 kendo olworore nyaka komachielo;
 onge gima opondo ne liet mare.

Koro angʼeyo ni Jehova Nyasaye reso ngʼate mowir;
 odwoke gie kare maler mar lemo manie polo,
 gi teko ma waro ji mar lwete ma korachwich.

Nikech ruoth ogeno kuom Jehova Nyasaye;
 kuom hera ma ok rum mar Nyasaye Man Malo Moloyo,
 ok obi yiengni.

Tekona osetwo ka balatago,
 kendo lewa omoko e danda;
 isepiela e lop tho.

Guogi oselwora;
 oganda mar joma richo oseketa diere,
 gisetucho lwetena gi tiendena.

Joma odhier biro chiemo mi yiengʼ;
 joma manyo Jehova Nyasaye biro pake,
 mad chunjeu bed mangima nyaka chiengʼ!

Jo-mwandu duto manie piny biro chiemo kendo lemo;
 ji duto madhi piny e lowo biro kulore e nyime,
 jogo ma ok nyal siko kangima.

tingʼuru lodiu malo, yaye dhorangeye;
 tingʼreuru malo, yaye rangeye machon,
 mondo Ruodh duongʼ odonji.

Tingʼuru lodiu malo, yaye un dhorangeye;
 tingʼ-giuru malo, un dhorangeye machon,
 mondo Ruodh duongʼ odonji.

Rit ngimana kendo iresa;
 kik iwe ane wichkuot,
 nikech in ema apondo kuomi.

Puonja yoreni, yaye Jehova Nyasaye;
 telna e yo moriere tir,
 nikech joma sanda.

Gen kuom Jehova Nyasaye;
 bed motegno ka in gi chir,
 kendo rit kuom Jehova Nyasaye.

Dwond Jehova Nyasaye mor ewi pige;
 Nyasaye mar duongʼ mor ka polo,
 Jehova Nyasaye mor ewi pige madongo.

Kuomi ema aseponde, yaye Jehova Nyasaye,
 kik iwe ayud wichkuot;
 gola e chandruok nikech timni makare.

Kecha, yaye Jehova Nyasaye, nikech an e chandruok;
 wengena ojony nikech ywak,
 kendo chunya gi ringra bende nigi lit.

Ndalona ni e lweti;
 resa e lwet wasika,
 kendo kuom joma lawa.

Mi dhogi mawacho miriambo mondo olingʼ;
 nikech sungagi kod chuny marach ma gin-go,
 omiyo giwuoyo gi wich teko kuom joma kare.

In e kar pondona;
 ibiro rita e chandruok,
 kendo ibiro lwora gi wende mag loch.  Sela

Ngʼat ma odhierni noluongo Jehova Nyasaye,
 kendo Jehova Nyasaye nowinje;
 ne orese mogole e chandruokne duto.

mad kethruok jukgi apoya ka gikia
 mad obadhogi ma gisechikona makgi;
 mad gilwar ei bur ma kargi lal nono.

To kane achwanyora, negichokore kaachiel gi mor;
 joma ne monja nochokorena sa ma ok angʼeyo,
 negisiko ka giketho nyinga.

Mad ji duto mamor nikech chandruokna
 oyud wichkuot kendo pachgi olal;
 mad joma kaworena oyud wichkuot gi achaya.

Kata konindo e kitandane, to ochano timo gima rach;
 oseketo chunye mar luwo yor richo,
 kendo ok otamre gima rach.

Bed mos e nyim Jehova Nyasaye, kendo rite kihori mos;
 kik chunyi chandre ka joma moko dhi nyime maber,
 ka gitimo chenrogi maricho.

Chunya nodoko maliet e iya
 kendo kane amedo paro matut, to nomedo bedo malit;
 eka ne atingʼo dhoga mi awuoyo:

Yaye Jehova Nyasaye, nyisa giko mar ngimana
 bende nyisa kar romb ndalona;
 mondo abed ka angʼeyo ni ndalona kadho piyo.

Iseketo ndalona obedo machiek ka bad dhano;
 kar romb higni maga ok gimoro e nyimi,
 ngima dhano ka dhano en mana muya nono.  Sela

Dhano en mana tipo makadho kata ka owuotho koni gi koni,
 orikni gi tijene mapile kayiem;
 ochoko mwandu mathoth ka ok ongʼeyo ngʼama obiro weyonegi.

Ikwero ji kikumogi nikech richogi;
 itieko mwandugi mana kaka thuth tieko oduma,
 dhano ka dhano en mana muya nono.  Sela

Ranyisi misetimo thoth,
 yaye Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasacha.
 Gigo mane ichanonwa
 onge ngʼama nyalo kwanoni;
 ka dine bed ni wanyalo wuoyo kuomgi;
 to dine gibedo mangʼeny ma ok wanyal wacho.

Alando tim makare e chokruok maduongʼ;
 ok aumo dhoga,
 mana kaka ingʼeyo, yaye Jehova Nyasaye.

Jehova Nyasaye biro rite kendo biro miyo obed mangima;
 Jehova Nyasaye biro gwedhe e piny,
 kendo ok obi jwangʼe e lwet wasike.

Jehova Nyasaye chiko herane godiechiengʼ,
 to gotieno to wende ni e chunya;
 ma e lamo ma alamogo Nyasach ngimana.

Ngʼadna bura makare, yaye Nyasaye,
 kendo chwaka e kind joma ok ongʼeyo Nyasaye;
 resa e lwet joma wuondore gi joma timbegi richo.

Chunya bedo mamor gi wer mamit
 e kinde mawero Zaburi maga ne Ruoth;
 kendo lewa chalo kalamb jandiko mongʼith.

