Ne iwacho e chunyi niya,
 “Abiro idho e polo;
 abiro guro lochna malo moyombo sulwe mag Nyasaye;
 kendo anabed e kom duongʼ,
 ewi got mar chokruok, mantiere malo mogik mar got maler.

“Abiro loko kar dakne ochal gi kar dak tula,
 kendo kar siany;
 mi anayweye oko kendo tieke chuth.”

E yore, girwako pien gugru;
 to ewi udi kod laru maduongʼ,
 giduto giywak ka gidengo kendo gingʼielore e lowo.

Kuonde ma pi luwo nodungʼ marach;
 bede aore mag Misri nodwon mi two.
 Odundu kod se biro ner,

Jolupo nobed gi lit mi ywagi,
 to jogo duto matego golowu e aora Nael;
 kod joma chiko gokgi e pi nosienyre.

Jotend Zoan osebedo joma ofuwo,
 jodong Memfis osewuondi;
 kendo jotelogi osewito jo-Misri.

Jehova Nyasaye osejwangʼogi ma chunygi ool;
 gimiyo jo-Misri tangni e gik moko duto ma otimo,
 machal mana ka jakongʼo madwanyore kama ongʼokie.

Jo-Elam kawo aserni mag-gi,
 kaachiel gi joriemb geche mag lweny gi farese;
 to jo-Kir to nokawo kuodigi.

E kindeno giniwach ni,
 “Adier ma en Nyasachwa;
 ne wageno kuome,
 kendo ne oresowa.
 Ma en Jehova Nyasaye, ne wageno kuome;
 wabeduru gi mor kendo gi ilo kuom warruokne.”

E ndalono wendni nower e piny Juda ni:
 Wan gi dala maduongʼ man-gi teko;
 Nyasaye kelo resruok e ohingane gi kuonde molwore.

To koro jogo osetho kendo koro gionge;
 chunje moseago ok nochier.
 Ne ikumogi mi itiekogi maonge ngʼama parogi.

Yaye Jehova Nyasaye,
 negimanyi e kinde mane ginie chandruok;
 kendo kane ikumogi ne gionge gi teko mar lemo.

Ka ok kamano to wegi gibi ira mondo abed kar pondogi;
 we mondo gilos kwe e kinda kodgi,
 ee, we gilos winjruok koda.”

Nadwoki piny miwuo mana koa ei lowo;
 kendo wecheni nowuog mana koa ei buru.
 Dwondi nochal mana ka dwond jachien moa ei lowo;
 kendo koa ei lowo dwondi nowinji.

Jehova Nyasaye osekelo nindo matut kuomu,
 oseumo wengeu (un jonabi);
 kendo oseumo wiyeu (un jokor wach).

Joma obolore nochak obed gi mor kuom Jehova Nyasaye;
 kendo joma ochando,
 bende nobed gi mor kuom Jal Maler mar Israel.

Joma timbegi mono nolal nono,
 jo-jar ji bende nolal nono,
 kendo jogo duto ma timbegi mono notieki;

Kuom mano ma e wach ma Jehova Nyasaye, mane oreso Ibrahim wachone od Jakobo ni,
 Jakobo ok none wichkuot kendo;
 bende ok ginichak ginenre mokuyo.

Tofeth noseiki nyaka aa chon;
 noseik ne ruoth.
 Kare mar kendo osekuny matut kendo malach,
 kodhurie yiende mangʼeny gi mach maduongʼ;
 kendo much Jehova Nyasaye,
 machalo mach makakni ema moke.

To jo-Misri gin mana dhano ma ok Nyasaye;
 bende faresegi gin mana ringʼo ma ok roho.
 Ka Jehova Nyasaye norie bade mar kum,
 jogo machiwo kony nochwanyre,
 kendo jogo mikonyo nopodh piny;
 giduto ginilal nono.

Mana kaka winy mafuyo malo,
 e kaka Jehova Nyasaye Maratego nochiel Jerusalem;
 nogengʼe kendo norese, noume kendo nokonye.

Beduru moluor un mon maparo nodak e ngima maber;
 beduru mokuyo, un nyiri maparo nodak gi kwe!
 Lonyreuru duge kendo utwe piende gugru enungou.

Enobed mise mar adier e ndalou,
 kar mwandu mar resruok gi rieko kod ngʼeyo;
 luoro Jehova Nyasaye e rayaw mar mwanduni.

Ka irango Sayun,
 dala maduongʼ mar sewniwa moyier;
 ibiro neno Jerusalem kama kwe nitie,
 hema ma ok bi muki;
 loje mage ok nopudhi, kata tondene ok nochodi.

Ok nokwe odiechiengʼ gotieno;
 iro mare nodum kanyo nyaka chiengʼ.
 Koa e tiengʼ moro nyaka machielo nodongʼ gunda;
 onge ngʼat manochak oluwe kendo.

Gi bungu norom gondiegi kuno,
 kendo diek mag bungu noywagne jowetegi;
 kanyo bende gik malich mag otieno noyud kar yweyo.

Enodogi mana gi yo mane obirogo;
 kendo ok enodonj e dala maduongʼni,”
 Jehova Nyasaye ema owacho.

Adier ogendini chalo mana ka pi matin modongʼ e dapi;
 ee, gichalo mana ka buru momoko e ratil,
 opimo chula mag nembe e ratil mana ka buru mayom.

Pinje manie chula oseneno wachno mi luoro omakogi;
 kendo tungʼ piny nyaka tungʼ piny kirni.
 Gibiro ka gisudo machiegni.

Omiyo kik ibed maluor, nimar an kodi;
 bende kik kibaji goyi, nimar an Nyasachi.
 Abiro miyi teko kendo abiro konyi;
 bende abiro siri gi bada ma korachwich mar loch.”

Kata obedo ni onenore kaka odundu mayom yom ok notur
 kendo kata obedo ni oliel ka taya ma mirimiri to ok notho.
 Enongʼad bura gadiera;

Anatel ne muofni mondo owuothi e yore mane ok gingʼeyo,
 kuonde mapok giwuothoe ema anatagie;
 kendo anami mudho olokrenegi ler,
 kendo analos kuonde bugni bed mopie.
 Magi e gik ma abiro timo;
 kendo ok najwangʼ-gi.

Kik ibed maluor, nimar an kodi;
 abiro duogo nyithindi koa yo wuok chiengʼ,
 kendo abiro choko nyithindi moa yo podho chiengʼ.

Parnauru gik mane otimore chon,
 mondo wapim wechego kanyakla;
 kendo wachuru ane gik manyiso ni uonge gi ketho.

En kaachiel gi joma chalo kode noyud wichkuot;
 kendo jopechogo gin mana dhano adhana.
 Wegiuru gichokre giduto mondo gichoma tir ane;
 ka ok giniyud wichkuot maduongʼ.

Onge gima gingʼeyo, onge gima giwinjo;
 wengegi omuon ti ma ok ginyal neno,
 kendo pachgi odinore ma ok ginyal winjo.

Ochamo buru, chunye mobam wuonde;
 ok onyal resore kende, kata wacho ni,
 “Donge gima ni e lweta korachwich ni miriambo?”

An e Jehova Nyasaye, kendo moro onge;
 onge Nyasaye moro makmana an.
 Anamiyi teko, kata obedo ni pok iyanga kamano,

An ema ne achweyo ler kod mudho,
 akelo gweth kod masira bende;
 An, Jehova Nyasaye ema timo magi duto.

Jogo duto maloso nyiseche manono
 noyud wichkuot kod achaya;
 kendo giduto gininwangʼ wichkuot.

“Biuru ira un joma oa e tungʼ
 piny gi tungʼ piny nimar unuyud resruok;
 nimar an Nyasaye, kendo onge moro amora.

Gipodho piny giduto;
 ma ok ginyal kelo resruok ne joma lamogi,
 ka gin giwegi otergi e twech.

Gitingʼe malo ma gikete e gokgi;
 eka gikete e kare monego obedie kendo kanyo ema osikoe.
 Kama oketeno ok onyal chorore.
 Kata bed ni ngʼato nyalo ywagorene to ok onyal dwoko;
 bende ok onyal rese e chandruokne.

In Nyar Babulon Mangili bed piny e buru;
 bed piny e lowo kionge loch in nyar jo-Babulon.
 Ok nochak oluongi ni nyako ma dende yom kendo ma jaber.

Kawuru nyiponge mondo ureg-go mogo;
 goluru leso ma uumogo wengeu.
 Ngʼwanuru lepu mondo ungʼadgo aore.

Ne akoro chon gik makoro osetimoregi,
 dhoga nohulogi mi namiyo gingʼere;
 bangʼe ne akelogi piyo magitimore.

Nimar nangʼeyo wich tekou;
 ka leche mag ngʼutu ochungʼ,
 kendo pat wengeu tek ka nyinyo.

Gin gik mochwe sani, kendo mapok obudho;
 bende gin gik mapok iwinjo nyaka chil kawuono.
 Omiyo ok inyal wacho ni, ‘Ee, ne angʼeyogi.’

Agengʼo mirimba nikech nyinga awuon;
 kendo ahora mondo arit pakna,
 mondo omi kik atieku.

Nyikwayi dine obedo mana ka kwoyo,
 to nyithindi dobedo mangʼeny mokalo akwana;
 nying-gi ok nongʼad oko kendo ok noruch e wangʼa.”

To ne, ginibi ka gia mabor;
 moko kawuok yo nyandwat, moko kawuok yo yimbo,
 moko to nowuogi e gwenge mag Aswan.”

To Sayun nowacho niya,
 “Jehova Nyasaye osejwangʼa;
 kendo Ruoth Nyasaye wiye osewil koda.”

Jehova Nyasaye Manyalo Gik Moko Duto oseyawo pacha
 kendo ok asetamore winjo wachne;
 bende ok asedok chien.

Jehova Nyasaye biro hoyo chuny Sayun adier;
 kendo obiro bedo gi kech kuom kuondene mokethore;
 enolok kuondene motimo ongoro chal ka Eden,
 kendo kuondene modongʼ gunda chal ka puoth Jehova Nyasaye.
 Mor gi ilo kaachiel gi erokamano
 gi wer mamit noyud kuome.

Joma ni e twech ma luoro omako ibiro gony machiegni;
 ok ginitho e kuondegi mag twech
 kendo ok ginichand chiemo.

To ok unuwuogi kurikni kata ka uringo;
 nimar Jehova Nyasaye notel nyimu,
 ee Nyasach Israel bende nodongʼnu chien.

Wan duto, waselal mana ka rombe,
 ka ngʼato ochomo mana yore owuon;
 kendo Jehova Nyasaye oseketo kuome richowa duto.

Kapo ni ngʼato omonji,
 to ok nobed ni an ema aore;
 to ngʼato angʼata momonji nochiwre e lweti.

Dwar Jehova Nyasaye ka pod thuolo
 nitie minyalo yudego;
 chutho luonge kapod en machiegni.

ei hekalu mara, anami nying-gi bedo rapar
 moloyo bedo gi yawuowi kod nyiri;
 bende anamigi nying ma ok norum nyaka chiengʼ.

Jorito mag Israel muofni,
 giduto gionge rieko;
 gichalo mana gi guogi mamuol,
 ma ok nyal giyo;
 kendo riere piny mi lek, nikech gihero nindo.

Tiendegi reto kadhi timo richo;
 giyot ahinya mondo gichwer remo maonge ketho.
 Paro manie chunygi gin paro maricho
 kendo kamoro amora ma gidhiyoe;
 masira gi chandruok ema dongʼie.

Kaka wuowi kendo nyako e kaka yawuoti nokendi;
 to bende kaka ngʼama okendo mor gi chiege,
 e kaka Nyasachi nobed mamor kodi.

Asenyono olemo mibiyo kenda;
 kendo ngʼato angʼata moa kuom ogendini mane ni koda.
 Ne anyonogi piny kakecho
 kendo ka an-gi mirima mager;
 mi rembgi okirore e lepa
 kendo omiyo lepa duto otimo remo.

Ne anyono ogendini kakecho;
 mi kuom mirimba ne amiyo gimer,
 kendo ne aolo rembgi e lowo.

Kata kamano, yaye Jehova Nyasaye, in e Wuonwa.
 Wan e lop chwech, to ine jachwechwa;
 kendo wan duto wan tich lweti.

gibet e dier liete joma otho otieno duto ka,
 gipondo kuonde mobuto, gichamo ring anguro,
 kendo agulnigi otingʼo chiemo moko makwero;

“To ne, wachno osiko kondiki e nyima ni:
 Ok analingʼ to abiro chulo kuor adimba;
 abiro chulo kuor kuneno,

Abiro kelo nyikwa joka Jakobo
 kendo joka Juda, jogo manokaw godena;
 ee joga mogen ma jotichna nokaw pinyno mi gidagie.

Abiro bedo gi mor gi Jerusalem
 kendo bedo gi ilo nikech joga;
 ywak kod koko mar nduru ok nochak owinji kuome kendo.

“Kapok muoch ochako kaye,
 to osenywolo nyathi;
 kapok owinjo rem to osenywolo wuowi.

Mana kaka miyo hoyo nyathine,
 e kaka abiro hoyou;
 kendo noho chunyu e Jerusalem.”

Jeremiah:
“Kane pok achweyi e ich ne angʼeyi,
 kane pok onywoli ne asewali tenge;
 ne ayieri kaka janabi ne pinje.”

Sibuoche oseruto;
 kendo gisemorne.
 Giseketho pinye;
 dalane owangʼ kendo odongʼ gunda.

Bende ubiro aa kanyo gi lweteu ka uketo ewiu,
 nimar Jehova Nyasaye osedagi joma ugeno kuomgi;
 ok ginikonyu.”

Ne angʼicho to piny
 mane miyo nolokore kama otwo;
 dalane duto nokethi e nyim mirimb Jehova Nyasaye mager.

To ne aparo ni, “Magi gin mana joma odhier;
 kendo gifuwo;
 nimar ok gingʼeyo yor Jehova Nyasaye
 kod dwaro mar Nyasachgi.

Giseriambo kuom Jehova Nyasaye;
 kagiwacho, “Onge gima obiro timo!
 Ok wanahinyre; ok wanane ligangla kata kech.

Jonabi chalo mana yamo
 kendo wach onge eigi;
 omiyo we gima giwacho otimre ne gin giwegi.”

Gigegi mitingʼoe asere
 chalo gi liel ma dhoge oyawore;
 giduto gin jolweny maroteke.

Jokwath kod jambgi noked kode;
 ginigur hembegi molwore,
 ka moro ka moro rito kare owuon.”

Bende gin-gi wichkuot kuom timbegi makwero?
 Ooyo, gionge wichkuot kata mana matin;
 ok gingʼeyo kata kaka ginyalo wuondore.
 Omiyo gibiro podho mana kaka joma moko mopodho;
 kendo ibiro dwokgi piny kakumogi,”
 Jehova Nyasaye owacho.

Omiyo winjuru, yaye un ogendini;
 ranguru malongʼo, yaye un joneno,
 gima biro timore negi.

Gimanore gi atungʼ kod tongʼ;
 giger kendo gionge ngʼwono.
 Gimor ka nam mogingore ka giriembo faresegi;
 gibiro ka ji mochanore komanore gi gige
 lweny mondo gimonju, yaye Nyar Sayun.”

Donge wigi kuot gi timbegi mamono?
 Ooyo, gionge wichkuot kata matin;
 bende gionge leny kata wichkuot.
 Omiyo ginipodhi e dier joma opodho;
 enolwargi piny ka ikumogi,
 Jehova Nyasaye owacho.

Idak e kind jo-miriambo;
 e wuondruokgino gisedagi yie kuoma.”
 Jehova Nyasaye ema owacho.

Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Maratego wacho:
 “Parane! Luonguru mon madengo mondo obi;
 to moloyo mago man-gi lony mamalo e ywak.

Koro, yaye mon,
 winjuru wach Jehova Nyasaye;
 yawuru itu ne weche mawuok e dhoge.
 Puonjuru nyiu dengo;
 puonjreuru ywak uwegi.

Nimar kit jogi kod timbegi onge tiende;
 gingʼado yien koa e bungu,
 bangʼe japecho paye gi koyo mare.

Giwire gi fedha gi dhahabu;
 giriwe motegno gi musmal ka gigoye gi nyundo,
 mondo kik oyiengni.

Mana kaka gima ibwogogo gik moko e puothe mag budho,
 e kaka nyisechegi manonogo ok nyal wuoyo;
 nyaka tingʼ-gi nikech ok ginyal wuotho.
 Kik uluorgi;
 ok ginyal hinyou
 kata timonu gima ber.”

To Jehova Nyasaye e Nyasaye madieri;
 en e Nyasaye mangima, Ruoth manyaka chiengʼ.
 Ka iye owangʼ, to piny tetni;
 ogendini ok nyal mirimbe.

To Nyasaye nochweyo piny gi tekone;
 ne ochako piny gi riekone,
 kendo oyaro polo gi ngʼeyo mare.

Ji duto parogi ok ti
 kendo gionge ngʼeyo;
 jotheth duto wigi
 kuot gi nyisechegi manono ma githedho.
 Kido mage moloso gin gik manono;
 gionge muya eigi.

Gionge tich, gin gik minyiero;
 ka ndalogi mar ngʼado bura ochopo,
 to ginilal nono.

Angʼeyo, yaye Jehova Nyasaye,
 ni ngima dhano ok en mare owuon;
 ok en mar dhano mondo ochik yorene.

Enobed puodho mojwangʼ,
 motwo, kendo machalo gunda e nyima;
 pinyno duto noyugno nikech onge ngʼama dewe.

Yaye Jehova Nyasaye,
 wayie gi timbewa mamono kod ketho mag wuonewa;
 adiera wasetimoni richo.

Ne kuom nyingi kik ijarwa;
 kik ijwangʼ kom duongʼ mari malich.
 Par singruok mari kodwa kendo kik ikethe.

To ka gipenji ni, ‘Ere kama wanyalo dhiyoe?’ To nyisgi ni, ‘Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho:
 “ ‘Mago matho ochomo, tho nonegi;
 mago ma ligangla ochomo, noneg gi ligangla;
 to mago ma kech ochomo, kech nonegi;
 to mago ma twech ochomo, noter e twech.’ ”

In ingʼeyo, yaye Jehova Nyasaye;
 para kendo konya.
 Chul kuor ne joma sanda.
 Isenano koda omiyo kik iweya;
 par kaka osesanda kochaya nikech in.

Pok aweyo bedo jakwath mari;
 ingʼeyo ni pok agombo odiechiengʼ mar thagruok.
 Gima wuok e dhoga ingʼeyo.

Mad jogo masanda ne wichkuot,
 to an kik wiya kuodi;
 mad gibed gi bwok maduongʼ
 to an kik ibwoga.
 Kel gigi kuomgi e kinde mar masira;
 kethgi gi kethruok manyadiriyo.

Omiyo we nyithindgi kech oka;
 bolgi e teko mar ligangla.
 We mondegi obed maonge nyithindo
 kendo mon ma chwogi otho;
 mad chwogi negi,
 rowere mag-gi negi gi ligangla e kedo.

Yaye Jehova Nyasaye, ne iwuonda kendo nowuonda;
 ne ihewa kendo iloya giteko.
 Itugo koda odiechiengʼ mangima;
 kendo ji duto nyiera.

To Jehova Nyasaye ni koda kaka jalweny maratego;
 omiyo jogo masanda nochwanyre kendo ok giniloya.
 Ok ginilo kendo ginibedi gi wichkuot malich;
 wichkuot margi wich ok nowil godo.

Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
 “Jonabi kod jodolo ok oluoro Nyasaye;
 kata mana ei hekalu mara ayudoe timbegi maricho.”

jopinje mamoko duto modak kanyo gi;
 ruodhi duto mar piny Uz;
 ruodhi duto mag jo-Filistia (mago mag Ashkelon, Gaza, Ekron kod jogo mane odongʼ Ashdod);

Ywaguru kendo denguru; un jokwath;
 ngʼielreuru e buru, un jokwadh rombe.
 Nimar sa mar negou osechopo;
 unupodhi kendo ungʼinjru matindo tindo,
 ka agulu molos mongʼith.

“ ‘To jogo duto motiekou notieki;
 wasiku duto noter e twech.
 Jogo momayou nomagi;
 jogo moketonu obadho anaketnegi obadho.

Ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho:
 “Jogo motony e ligangla noyud ngʼwono e piny motimo ongoro;
 anabi mondo ami Israel yweyo.”

Jehova Nyasaye nofwenyorenwa chon, kawacho niya:
 “Aseherou gihera manyaka chiengʼ;
 aseomou gihera mar ngʼwono.

Ogendini nowinj wichkuot momaki;
 ywakni nopongʼ piny.
 Jolweny nochwanyre kuom moro ka moro;
 giduto ginipodhi kanyakla.”

Ginichwanyre moluwore oluwore;
 giniluowre kuom jowetegi.
 Giniwachi ni, ‘Aa malo,
 wadog ir jowa wawegi;
 kendo e pinywa owuon,
 mabor gi ligangla mar joma thiro ji.’

Ruoth, ma nyinge Jehova Nyasaye Maratego wacho niya,
 “Moab nokethi kendo mier mage nomonji;
 yawuote mabeyo noter e kar nek.

Tung Moab ongʼad oko;
 bade otur,”
 Jehova Nyasaye ema owacho.

“Omiyo chunya ywagorene Moab ka asili;
 oywagore ka asili ne jo-Kir Hareseth.
 Mwandu mane giyudo oserumo.

“Edom nobed gima bwogo ji;
 jogo duto makalo bute nohum nono,
 kendo gininyiere ka gineno adhondene duto.”

Adiera, joge matindo nopodh e yore;
 jolweny mage duto nolingʼ thi odiechiengno,”
 Jehova Nyasaye Maratego owacho.

“Ringuru uwuog Babulon;
 ayeuru e piny jo-Babulon,
 kendo uchal gi diek motelone jamni.

Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
 “Omiyo Babulon noyaki;
 jogo moyake nokaw gik moromogi.

To anaduog Israel e kare
 mar kwath kendo enokwa e Karmel kod Bashan;
 noyiengʼ e gode matindo mag Efraim gi Gilead.”

Achikonu obadho,
 yaye Babulon, kendo nomaku kapod ok ungʼeyo;
 noyudu kendo omaku nikech ne ukwedo Jehova Nyasaye.

Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya,
 “Emomiyo, joge matindo nogore piny e yore;
 jolweny mage duto nonegi odiechiengno.”

Kata kamano Jawar margi en ratego;
 Jehova Nyasaye Maratego e nyinge.
 Enokonygi gi nyalone duto
 mondo omi gibed gi yweyo e pinygi;
 to jo-Babulon nomi obed gi tungni.”

Gimanore gi atungʼ kod tongʼ;
 giger kendo gionge ngʼwono.
 Gimor ka nam mogingore
 ka giriembo faresegi;
 gibiro ka ji mochanore komanore
 gi gige lweny mondo gimonju, yaye Nyar Babulon.

“ ‘Jehova Nyasaye oseketowa joma kare;
 biuru, we wawache ei Sayun,
 gima Jehova Nyasaye, ma Nyasachwa osetimo.’

“Nochweyo piny gi tekone;
 ne ochako piny gi riekone,
 kendo oyaro polo gi ngʼeyo mare.

“Ji duto parogi ok ti kendo gionge ngʼeyo;
 jotheth duto wigi kuot gi nyisechegi manono, ma githedho.
 Kido mage moloso gin gik manono;
 gionge muya eigi.

Jolwenj Babulon oseweyo kedo;
 gidongʼ e kuondegi mochiel motegno mag lweny.
 Tekogi orumo; gisebedo ka mon.
 Kuondegi mag dak osemoke mach;
 lodi mage mag rangeye otur.

Emomiyo, ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho:
 “Ne, anabed jakori kendo anakonyi e bura;
 anami nembe two kendo thidhna mage notwo.

Jehova Nyasaye noketh Babulon;
 nomi koko olingʼ thi.
 Apaka mag wasigu nowuo ka pige mopongʼ;
 koko mar dwondgi nowinjre kendo.

Jaketh nobi ketho Babulon;
 jolweny mage nomaki,
 kendo atungʼ mag-gi notur.
 Nimar Jehova Nyasaye en Nyasaye
 machulo kuor ni ji kuom richogi;
 enochul duto.”

Lamentations:
Wasiki duto
 wuoyo marach kuomi;
 gijari ka gikayo lekegi
 kagiwacho niya, “Wasetieke chuth.
 Ma e ndalo mane wasebedo ka warito;
 adier, osechopo ma wanene.”

Ezekiel:
Wasigu ni oko gi ligangla;
 to tuoche kod kech ni e mier.
 Joma ni e gwengʼ
 noneg gi ligangla;
 to joma ni ei dala maduongʼ
 kech gi tuoche nonegi.

To kata kamano, ne opudhe gi mirima mager
 mi ogoye piny.
 Yamo ma aa yo wuok chiengʼ nomiyo oner;
 olembege ne olwer mogol kuome;
 kendo bedene maroteke bende notwo
 mi mach nowangʼogi.

Gone oganda mohero ngʼanyoni ngeroni, kendo wach nigi ni ma e gima Jehova Nyasaye Manyalo Gik Moko Duto wacho:
 “ ‘Ket aguch tedo e kendo;
 kendo iol pi e iye.

Ket ringʼo mosengʼadi matindo tindo e iye,
 ringʼo machwe duto; ma gin em gi bat.
 Pongʼe gi choke machwe duto;

Asetemo konye motamore;
 chilo momoko kuome pek ma ok wuogi,
 kata wangʼ gi mach.

Jo-Arvad kod jo-Helek
 nolworo ohingani koni gi koni karito;
 Jo-Gamad noidho wi uteu
 moger maboyo mag rito.
 Ne gingʼawo okumbnigi molworo ohinga magi;
 kendo negimiyo berni obedo malongʼo chuth.

Jo-ohala madongo manie pinje mamoko liyo ka wuoro;
 giko mari obedo marach miwuoro,
 kendo ok nochak oneni kendo.’ ”

Abiro moko mach kuom Misri;
 to Pelusiuma biro bedo gi rem malit.
 Koth maduongʼ nochwe Thebes mamuk ohinga mare;
 to Memfis biro bedo gi chandruok ma ok rum.

Hosea:
Koro abiro nyiso ayanga gombo mare mar chode
 e lela e nyim joherane;
 kendo onge ngʼama nogole e lweta.

Abiro timo kodi singruok mar kend mondo ibed mara chuth;
 abiro timo kodi singruok mar kend e yo maler kendo maratiro,
 gihera kod kech.

Abiro pidhe e piny ne an awuon;
 abiro nyiso herana ni ngʼat mane aluongo ni ‘Ok jaherana.’
 Anawach ni joma iluongo ni,
 ‘Joma ok joga,’ ni, ‘Un joga’;
 kendo ginidwoka ni, ‘In Nyasachwa.’ ”

Kaka jodolo medore,
 e kaka gimedo timo richo e nyima;
 gisewilo duongʼ margi gi gima kelo wichkuot.

Kata ka kong-gi orumo,
 to gidhi nyime gi timbegi mag chode;
 jotendgi ohero timbe makelo wichkuot.

Angʼeyo gik moko duto kuom Efraim;
 onge gima opondona kuom jo-Israel.
 Efraim, un to usedoko kaka ochot;
 to jo-Israel timo timbe modwanyore.

Sungruok mar jo-Israel nyiso rachgi;
 jo-Israel kaachiel gi Efraim podho e richogi;
 kendo jo-Juda bende podho kodgi.

Waluonguru Jehova Nyasaye;
 wadhiuru nyime gi luongo nyinge.
 Mana kaka chiengʼ wuok,
 e kaka obiro wuok;
 enobi irwa mana ka kodh chwiri,
 mana ka koth mabiro bangʼ chwiri mamiyo lowo bedo mangʼich.”

Emomiyo an kaachiel gi jonabi maga wangʼadou matindo tindo,
 ne anegou gi weche mawuok e dhoga;
 buche mane angʼadonu nobiro kuomo mapiyo mana ka mil polo.

Israel osetiek duto;
 kendo sani en e kind ogendini,
 mana kaka gima nono.

Kik umor, yaye Israel;
 bende kik ubed gi ilo kaka ogendini mamoko.
 Nimar ok usebedo jo-adiera ne Nyasachu;
 usehero chudo mar ochot michulougo,
 e kuonde dino cham.

Ok ginidongʼ e piny Jehova Nyasaye;
 Efraim nodog Misri,
 kendo ginicham chiemo ma ok opwodhi e piny Asuria.

Ok gini olne Jehova Nyasaye misango mar divai,
 bende misengini ma gichiwo ok nomor Jehova Nyasaye ngangʼ.
 Misengini machalo kamano nochal negi mana kaka chiemb joma ywak;
 kendo jogo mochamogi nobed mogak.
 Chiemoni nobed margi giwegi;
 omiyo ok nokele e hekalu mar Jehova Nyasaye.

Israel ne en mzabibu malandore;
 ne onyago olembene owuon.
 Ka olembene ne medore,
 nomedo gero kende mag misango;
 kendo ka pinye ne medo mewo,
 to nomedo loso kido milamo.

Ka ahero to abiro kumogi;
 ogendini nonywaknegi,
 maketgi e twech kuom richogi duto.

Jehova Nyasaye nigi bura kuom jo-Juda;
 enokum Jakobo kaluwore gi yorene;
 kendo enochule kaluwore gi timbene.

To nyaka uduog ir Nyasachu;
 beduru johera kendo joma ngʼado bura makare,
 bende keturu chunyu kuom Nyasachu kinde duto.

Jakobo noringo modhi e piny mar Aram;
 Israel notiyo mondo oyud dhako,
 kendo nochulo nengo mare kokwayo rombe.

To Efraim osemiye obedo mager mobedo gi mirima;
 Ruodhe nowe timbene maricho mag chwero remo e wiye,
 kendo nochule kuom ngʼanyone.

Kane apidhogi ne giyiengʼ chuth;
 kane giseyiengʼ to sunga nomakogi;
 ma wigi owil koda.

Anachal mana ka thoo mar okinyi ne Israel;
 kendo nolodhi mana ka ondanyo,
 kendo tiende nokar
 mana ka yiend Lebanon;

Joel:
Yaye piny, weuru luor;
 bed mamor kendo moil,
 adiera Jehova Nyasaye osetimo gik madongo.

Yaye le manie thim, weuru luor;
 nikech pewe kwath koro loth,
 yiende nyago olembegi;
 Ngʼowu gi mzabibu golo mwandugi.

“Abiro chulou kuom higni ma bonyo osechamo;
 bonyo madongo gi matindo,
 gi bonyo mamoko gi mony mar bonyo;
 ma gin oganda maduongʼ mar jolweny mara mane aoro e dieru.

Jehova Nyasaye noruti koa Sayun
 kendo nomor koa Jerusalem.
 Piny gi Polo noyiengni;
 to Jehova Nyasaye nobed kar pondo mar joge;
 nobed ragengʼ ne jo-Israel.

Amos:
“Kuonde lemo duto mag joka Isaka ibiro kethi
 kendo kuonde maler duto mag Israel ibiro kethi;
 kendo anabi gi ligangla mondo aked gi dhood Jeroboam.”

Obadiah:
Ogendini ma uriworugo biro sembou nyaka giko mar tongʼ;
 osiepeu biro wuondou ma lowu;
 kendo joma chamo chiembu biro ketonu obadho,
 to ok unufweny.”

Nikech lweny mane utimone owadu Jakobo
 unubed gi wichkuot;
 mi nokethu nyaka chiengʼ.

Micah:
Gige mopa molamo ibiro toyo matindo tindo;
 kendo mich mag hekalu mochiwo ibiro wangʼ gi mach;
 abiro ketho kido mage molos duto.
 Nikech michgo nochoko koa e chudo mar ochot,
 omiyo koro ibiro ti kodgi kaka chudo mar ochot.”

Jonabi mag-gi wacho niya, “Kik ukor wach.
 Kik ukor wach kuom gigi;
 wichkuot ok nomakwa.”

Umon gi gik mabeyo to uhero gik maricho;
 ukidho pien joga oko
 ka uyiecho ringʼo oko e chokegi.

Winj gima Jehova Nyasaye wacho:
 “Chungʼ malo, ket kwayoni e nyim gode;
 thuche mondo owinj wach ma in-go.

Anto amanyo Jehova Nyasaye gi wangʼa ka an kod geno,
 arito Nyasaye ma Jawarna;
 kendo Nyasacha biro winja.

Nahum:
Nineve to obiro ywero,
 gi ohula maduongʼ motiek chuth;
 obiro lawo joma kwede nyaka e mudho mandiwa.

Gimoro amora marach ma gichano timo ni Jehova Nyasaye
 obiro tieko;
 bende chandruok ok nobedie kendo.

Okumba mag jolweny osebedo makwar ka remo;
 kendo lewni ma girwakorego bende kwar.
 Chuma manie ewi gechegi mil
 ka giikore ne chiengʼ lweny;
 tongegi opiag mabith kendo milni ka gikedogo.

Ne jolweny magi;
 gin mana mon lilo!
 Dhorangeye mag dalani
 oyaw malich ni wasiki;
 mach osewangʼogi.

Habakkuk:
“Ne kaka osungore;
 dwarone ok nikare.
 To ngʼat makare nobed mangima kuom yie mare,

Jehova Nyasaye, asewinjo humbi;
 achungʼ e nyimi ka an-gi luoro kuom gik misetimo, yaye Jehova Nyasaye.
 Mad itimgi kendo e kindewa,
 mi gingʼere e ndalowani;
 ka in gi mirima to mad ipar ngʼwono.

Berne ne chalo kawuok chiengʼ;
 kendo ler ne mil ka wuok e lwete,
 kama tekone opandie.

gode ne oneni ma otetni giluoro;
 oula nomwomo karidore.
 Kude matut bende mor matek;
 apaka ne tingʼore malo.

Wangʼ chiengʼ gi dwe nochungʼ kargi e kor polo
 ka gineno asernigi mibayo;
 ka mil polo machalo tongʼ mobaa.

Zechariah:
Turo osegero kar pondo mare motegno;
 kendo osechoko fedha,
 gi dhahabu modhurore ka pith.

Yaye yiend obudo, go nduru,
 nimar yiend sida osepodho;
 kendo yiende maboyo mabeyo oselwar piny.
 Un yiend ober mag Bashan;
 go nduru, nimar bungu ma yien ngʼenyie osebet oko.

Jehova Nyasaye owacho niya,
 “E piny ngima, ariyo kuom adek mar ji biro tho mi ngʼad kargi oko;
 to kata kamano, achiel kuom adek mar jogo to nowe kangima.

Luke:
Nimar ondiki niya,
 “ ‘Obiro miyo malaika mage chik nikech in
 mondo oriti maber;

Hebrews:
Isehero tim makare to imon gi timbe maricho;
 emomiyo Nyasaye ma Nyasachi osetingʼi malo moyombo jowadu,
 nikech osewiri gi mo mamiyi mor.”

Revelation of John:
Nimar Nyarombo mobedo e kom loch mar Nyasaye nobed jakwadhgi;
 notelnigi koterogi e sokni mag pi ngima,
 to Nyasaye noywe pi wangʼ-gi duto.”
